rComments: Great TA! If you are in Calc III, you should have him as a TA, because he is the best from all others. He gives good examples in class and always welcome to help you with any question.

He knows the subject very well. And is more than willing to help if you have questions. As in any math class the material in not exciting.  But haveing him as a TA will help you get a better grade in the class.
